<i>(Court of the Crosswinds)</i>, wizard and follower of Tunare</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uzalikfv.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ZalikFV</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/22/02 5:09:29 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1162.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Recruiting</span><hr size=1> Recruiting is a off and on thing. You have to really be a good judge of character. Even more so on this server cause people are roleplaying, so alot of times you dont see their true sides tell later on.<br>
