<br>
But yeah.  I interviewed them.  And I made it very clear that while we would help them, we weren't going to twink them and that we weren't concerned with powergaming.  I also tried to make sure that they understood what RP we were aiming for (sadly, EQ's own lack of support through faction is what caused the death of Lords of Discipline). <p><center><font size=+2><a href="http://pub66.ezboard.com/bmaidensfancy">Shiden Kaidan</a></font>
